column1: #: description: J/psi-->mu+mu- and J/psi-->e+e- nuclear modification in Cu+Cu collisions as a function of p_T at forward and mid-rapidity for the 0-20 centrality range. The statistical and systematic uncertainties vary point-to-point and are listed for each measured value.  An additional global systematic uncertainty is provided in each column heading, which applies to all data points per column.
